DESCRIPTION:Description Every second Tuesday of the month\, we get together
	 downstairs at a/stir to read original works of art\, whether it is an ess
	ay\, short story\, poem or comedy routine. Just bring your stuff\, or just
	 listen. Don't worry\, our resident writer\, former service lead\, Jen wil
	l start the proceedings to warm you up. 7-9pm. All ages. No cover.\n\nhttp
